comment: Hansbrough (TOR) and Vucevic (ORL) briefly engage away from the ball and then separate immediately.
Lowry (TOR) and Oladipo (ORL) make incidental foot to foot contact after Oladipo passes the ball.
Hansbrough (TOR) clamps Vucevic's (ORL) arm and affects his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Fournier (ORL) steps OOB after catching the pass.
Hansbrough (TOR) and Vucevic (ORL) briefly engage during rebounding.
Payton (ORL) maintains legal guarding position as he defends the play to the basket by DeRozan (TOR).
Patterson (TOR) sets the screen on Harris (ORL) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Vucevic (ORL) maintains legal guarding position and does not affect DeRozan's (TOR) RSBQ on the baseline drive.
Lowry (TOR) commits a take foul on Payton (ORL).
Vasquez (TOR) and DeRozan (TOR) cleanly contest Vucevic's (ORL) tip-in attempt.
